  "body": "Reproduction repo: https://github.com/fvictorio/hardhat-symlink-bug\r\n\r\nClone and run the steps in the readme.\r\n\r\nNotice that `dependency/contracts/dir2/link` is a symlink. This seems to be the root of the problem.\r\n\r\nAs part of this fix, we should remove all non-null assertions like these and use `assertHardhatInvariant` instead:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/nomiclabs/hardhat/blob/677099d520a3756929145ff450dfd7d39babf036/packages/hardhat-core/src/internal/solidity/dependencyGraph.ts#L113-L114",
